[
    {
        "url": "/quotes/gerard_arpey_373929",
        "quote": "These are times of unprecedented challenge and change in the airline industry, and the appointments we are announcing today will put American in an even stronger position to continue the substantial progress that has already been made under the tenets of our Turnaround Plan.",
