                "url": "/topics/integrating"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/gerard_arpey_373907",
        "quote": "However, the economics of our business continued to deteriorate. We barely escaped bankruptcy a year ago, and in the aftermath of that escape we had to make some even tougher decisions.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Gerard Arpey",
            "url": "/quotes/gerard_arpey_373907"
