                "url": "/topics/however"
            }
        ]
    },
    {
        "url": "/quotes/gerard_arpey_373908",
        "quote": "One of our most difficult realizations was that - in the course of two years - a connecting hub in St. Louis had gone from something we thought we needed to something we could no longer afford.",
        "author": {
            "name": "Gerard Arpey",
            "url": "/quotes/gerard_arpey_373908"
